headline: Is the Artificial Intelligence Boost Fading for This Top Tech Stock?
summary: Workday's first-quarter performance was good, but obviously not good enough to impress many investors.  The market tends to expect giant leaps from businesses that are knee-deep in artificial intelligence technology.  When artificial intelligence (AI) stocks were all the rage earlier this year, next-generation human resources solutions developer Workday's (NASDAQ: WDAY) stock enjoyed a bit of a spring rally.
